  "1879860": {
    "name": "Fractured Worlds",
    "steam_appid": 1879860,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Fractured Worlds》是一款黑暗奇幻风格的动作角色扮演游戏，故事发生在因人类野心而四分五裂的现实世界中。现在，在神秘声音的引导下，你必须踏上探索破碎世界的旅程，拼凑过去的真相，并直面导致这场灾难的幕后黑手。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>深思熟虑、精准为本的战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种武器都有其独特的重量、速度和动作组合。从攻击缓慢但能击晕敌人的双手巨锤，到适合控场的灵活长矛，再到掌控以太流动的魔法法杖——每种武器的手感与玩法都大不相同。无职业限制的成长系统允许多次重置加点，让你轻松尝试各种战斗风格，或围绕你获得的强大传奇装备打造专属角色构筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/8ca131990a982291e8684159eed9874d.poster.avif?t=1768143107\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/8ca131990a982291e8684159eed9874d.webm?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/8ca131990a982291e8684159eed9874d.mp4?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>邂逅其他玩家</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现实的扭曲意味着其他玩家的世界可能会与你的短暂交叠。你可以选择与他们互动，或者独自前行。你可以入侵或支援，帮助或欺骗，分享一处丰富的战利品，或引诱他们进入致命的怪物群中，并在战斗结束后收割成果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/1b129af12710e9f813940b95ef88d609.poster.avif?t=1768143107\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/1b129af12710e9f813940b95ef88d609.webm?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/1b129af12710e9f813940b95ef88d609.mp4?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索多样破碎的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入由过去世界碎片构成的独特程序生成环境。穿越中世纪地牢、神秘魔法森林、火山地貌与未来工业城市。寻找记忆碎片，揭示灾变中受害者的故事，帮助你理解真相并修复这个支离破碎的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/df3248efc423098c574e6abbe45420df.poster.avif?t=1768143107\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/df3248efc423098c574e6abbe45420df.webm?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/df3248efc423098c574e6abbe45420df.mp4?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>分享你世界的一部分</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图碎片是强大的神器，可让玩家将自己世界的一部分与他人共享。地图碎片会生成一个带有随机词缀的合作实例，能以不可预测的方式改变怪物属性，并提升他们守护的战利品质量。当你与他人共享地图时，还可以留下评论，让其他玩家了解该区域的情况——是满地宝藏，还是异常凶险的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/de8ab6de3a6dcb31038d7aebe2028279.poster.avif?t=1768143107\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/de8ab6de3a6dcb31038d7aebe2028279.webm?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/de8ab6de3a6dcb31038d7aebe2028279.mp4?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑战强大首领</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对阻挡你前路的强大首领。挑战宝藏魔像、精神扭曲者罗尔施、威严的幽灵骑士，以及更多恐怖敌人。每场首领战都是严峻而致命的挑战，一次失误就可能让你损失大量生命值。但这些战斗都经过精心设计，攻击前会有清晰的预警信号，只要多加练习，即使是最强敌人也能被你击败。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/d4a2f2570bd8cd40fbe01b5867853a56.poster.avif?t=1768143107\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/d4a2f2570bd8cd40fbe01b5867853a56.webm?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879860/extras/d4a2f2570bd8cd40fbe01b5867853a56.mp4?t=1768143107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Fractured Worlds》带来一段穿越破碎现实的旅程，专注于爽快的战斗与重建失落世界的使命。</p>",
